{"tid":729532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Maryknoll套校服真係咁正? 今日搭地鐵比個靚仔抽我水...","createTime":"2018-07-04T15:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T02:59:19.000Z","uid":112742,"like":22,"dislike":357,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2a778031b52a1c66ef0b916e45f96bfc5ad80a7e","tid":729532,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:34:14.000Z","msg":"我讀Maryknoll既 都算半間名校啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能套校服下身cutting特別現pat 成日好吸引人目光<br />\n但我好鍾意比人昅...見到人昅自己就會好想要...<br />\n由細到大Miss都叫我地要檢點D 所以即使好大食都唔好表露出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今朝搭緊地鐵上車果陣已經見到個180靚仔既望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搭搭下好多人上左車所以個靚仔逼左埋來 <br />\n搭多幾個站Feel到有佢用碌鳩頂我屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇避開 反而仲壓落去磨左幾下<br />\n到左觀塘落車行返學果陣先發現自己都濕哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e3a139a711282266e2e478a88808b4db7d1348","tid":729532,"uid":132587,"like":552,"dislike":13,"score":539,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:35:17.000Z","msg":"男人老狗著女校校服盲既都望啦"},{"pid":"47391400eebc64fe7fef4ef6c8f64a989a54c05a","tid":729532,"uid":19978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"478c5d91226ed939dfd78b4e7b739e012eac6e58","tid":729532,"uid":95542,"like":238,"dislike":0,"score":238,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"觀瑪＝男校<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afd50afdd55ac6ef795bd811a441d4d05ccc4fe","tid":729532,"uid":9411,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:38:10.000Z","msg":"之前同ex一定要著校服扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/